<p>A container element which can contain any number of child elements. This is equivalent to the <code><span class="script">XULElem("box")</span></code> element.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/The_Box_Model" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/The_Box_Model">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
<h3>Example</h3>
<pre>
&lt;!-- Two button on the right --&gt;
&lt;hbox&gt;
  &lt;spacer flex="1"/&gt;
  &lt;button label="Connect"/&gt;
  &lt;button label="Ping" /&gt;
&lt;/hbox&gt;
</pre>
